Distribution.
We found this species to be widespread and recorded it from Deception Island down to Jenny Island in the South. At some sites it was very abundant, notably Port Circumcision, Pieterman Island. 

Myxilla asigmata

is widespread in the Antarctic and Subantarctic: Bellingshausen Sea (
